{"tid":1967892,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★04月11日】西貢海傍食肆幾近滿座","createTime":"2020-04-11T09:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T11:38:15.000Z","uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"adbd92c3d2f437df8500efbd8212c7ecc562dbf0","tid":1967892,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T09:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4308333/org/1cf40225948e51fdbee591e7e51a93ec.jpeg/I8mY5opkwNBL3hrC0S6lovoJaOrWkHRECWx24yNsduM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4308333%2Forg%2F1cf40225948e51fdbee591e7e51a93ec.jpeg%2FI8mY5opkwNBL3hrC0S6lovoJaOrWkHRECWx24yNsduM&h=06ff62b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4308576/org/4de529d0231fc7fc440413abe45bb13e.jpeg/kpd6mrvylw_tvW57jdtHzjqirCcF0MDB5nnMSeZ5zEk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4308576%2Forg%2F4de529d0231fc7fc440413abe45bb13e.jpeg%2Fkpd6mrvylw_tvW57jdtHzjqirCcF0MDB5nnMSeZ5zEk&h=599b0059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n踏入復活節假第二日，雖然政府呼籲市民盡量留在家中，但不少人仍然到郊外遊玩。西貢市中心一帶人流興旺，海傍一帶的海鮮酒樓在中午時間幾乎坐滿。有市民直言，約一個半月以來，未有與家人出外用膳，特意假日期間與家人到戶外走走，在海傍食肆用餐。有酒家經理表示，這兩日生意額較「限聚令」及「限客令」剛推出時多約三分之一，但形容僅屬「虛火」，疫情之下，生意今非昔比。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/459831/%E5%BE%A9%E6%B4%BB%E7%AF%80-%E8%A5%BF%E8%B2%A2%E6%B5%B7%E5%82%8D%E9%A3%9F%E8%82%86%E5%B9%BE%E8%BF%91%E6%BB%BF%E5%BA%A7-%E7%B6%93%E7%90%86-%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F%E5%8D%87%E4%B8%89%E6%88%90%E5%83%85-%E8%99%9B%E7%81%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F459831%2F%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%25B2%25A2%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%2582%258D%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%2582%2586%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E8%25BF%2591%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E5%25BA%25A7-%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%2590%2586-%25E7%259